<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Urban planners and regional developers shape the physical landscapes of our communities. The <span class="title-main">Sustainable Environmental Design </span>major prepares students to thoughtfully plan communities, design livable cities, develop smooth-running transportation systems and create healthy, equitable urban spaces.</p>
